evaluation_data.role_requirements:
For the role of a Machine Learning Junior, here are the relevant technical skills, programming languages, frameworks, and tools:

LANGUAGES: 
- Python
- R
- SQL

FRAMEWORKS: 
- TensorFlow
- PyTorch
- scikit-learn
- Keras
- FastAPI (for deploying models)

TOOLS: 
- Jupyter Notebook
- Anaconda
- Git
- Docker (for containerization)
- MLflow (for model tracking)
- Pandas (for data manipulation)
- NumPy (for numerical computations)
- Matplotlib/Seaborn (for data visualization)

KEYWORDS: 
- Machine Learning
- Data Preprocessing
- Feature Engineering
- Model Evaluation
- Supervised Learning
- Unsupervised Learning
- Neural Networks
- Hyperparameter Tuning
- Cross-Validation
- Data Science
